headline: Deere's Stock Has Been Hot Lately. It Took a Breather Today
summary: Shares of tractor and farm equipment maker Deere have been on a tear this year, recently touching record highs. They dipped today.

headline: Prediction: These 3 Monster Dividend Stocks Will Continue Crushing the S&P 500 Beyond 2025
summary: Deere is delivering strong results despite a choppy operating environment.  Sunoco recently announced the acquisition of Parkland -- a transaction that will provide immediate benefits.  Three Motley Fool contributors were asked to outline why Deere (NYSE: DE), Cheniere Energy Partners L.P. (NYSE: CQP), and Sunoco L.P. (NYSE: SUN) are three dividend stocks that can continue outperforming the S&P 500 (SNPINDEX: ^GSPC) beyond 2025.
